OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,FA hospice in Dorset is calling for an
OL,7,Fend to what they say is an unfair
OL,8,Fpostcode lottery of funding which sees
OL,9,Fthem receive just 8% of their budget
OL,10,Ffrom the government.
OL,12,FJulia's House helps nearly 200
OL,13,Ffamilies across Dorset and Wiltshire -
OL,14,Fincluding that of eight year old Blake
OL,15,Fwho has a rare neuro-developmental
OL,16,Fcondition which means she is unable to
OL,17,Fwalk or talk.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,FThe hospice at Corfe Mullen in Dorset
OL,7,Fprovides the family activity sessions,
OL,8,Fsupport for Blake's older sister - and
OL,9,Fcrucial respite to give her parents
OL,10,Frare time off together.
OL,12,FMum Amber Spillard fears without long
OL,13,Fterm funding commitment the services
OL,14,Fthey benefit from are at risk.
OL,16,F"It makes me feel terrified," she said.
OL,18,F"We live on a knife edge anyway,
OL,19,Fcontinually frightened that things are
OL,20,Fgoing to disappear or fighting for
OL,21,Fthings that we just need to survive."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"Locally, there's been some recent
OL,7,Fclosures of other hospices so in our
OL,8,Farea -It's so imperative what they do.
OL,10,F"I don't know what we'd do without it."
OL,12,FSo far Julia's House has not had to
OL,13,Fmake cuts to frontline services - but
OL,14,Fthey have a #1 million budget deficit
OL,15,Fthis year. They say costs have risen
OL,16,Fby about 20%.
OL,18,FThe Deputy Chief Executive Mike
OL,19,FBartlett said: "We support nearly 200
OL,20,Fchildren and their families across two
OL,21,Fcounties.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"And from a funding perspective, the
OL,7,Fdemand for our services is going up.
OL,8,FWe're supporting more children than
OL,9,Fever. The needs are greater than ever.
OL,10,FAnd in real terms, the funding across
OL,11,Fthe whole county and across the
OL,12,Fcountry is declining."
OL,14,FMr Bartlett said that because of the
OL,15,Fway hospice services are commissioned
OL,16,Fand paid for they have to rely much
OL,17,Fmore heavily on public donations than
OL,18,Fin other parts of the country - more
OL,19,Fthan 90% of their funding comes from
OL,20,Ffundraising and gifts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"Currently we only get 8% of our
OL,7,Ffunding from government, which is one
OL,8,Fof the lowest in the country. And the
OL,9,Fsustainability of our service is
OL,10,Freliant on sustainable funding.
OL,12,F"There's a postcode lottery where
OL,13,Fevery hospice is competing for funds
OL,14,Fwith local commissioners."
OL,16,FA report released this week from the
OL,17,Forganisation Together for Short Lives
OL,18,Fsays 60 per cent of hospices are now
OL,19,Frunning a deficit.
OL,21,FIt also found that:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,FResponding to the picture the report
OL,7,Fillustrates, Mike Barlett said: "In a
OL,8,Fway it tells us what we know. It tells
OL,9,Fus that children's hospices are
OL,10,Fstruggling... and the funding
OL,11,Fsituation isn't changing.
OL,13,F"I think it's unfair on the families
OL,14,Fthat we care for because we want to
OL,15,Fplan. We want to plan for the future.
OL,16,FMany of the children we look after, we
OL,17,Flook after them for many years, and we
OL,18,Fcan't plan their care.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,FBlake's mother Amber said that they've
OL,7,Fbeen receiving help and support from
OL,8,FJulia's House for three years.
OL,10,F"It's an invaluable resource for my
OL,11,Ffamily," she said. "When we first came
OL,12,Fwe were struggling across the board,
OL,13,Freally.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"It sounds dramatic, but it did save
OL,7,Fus because we were a very low point.
OL,8,FIt does. When you have a child with
OL,9,Fsuch a severe disability, it does
OL,10,Fchange your friendship groups and
OL,11,Falienate you from society a little and
OL,12,Fmeeting other people and knowing that
OL,13,Fwe're not alone really did save us."
OL,15,FShe said that Blake has benefited
OL,16,Fhugely since coming to the hospice for
OL,17,Factivity sessions. She loves music and
OL,18,Fenjoying the swings outside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"It took her a little while to get
OL,7,Fused to coming here but now she lights
OL,8,Fup the minute we get here. I am sure
OL,9,Fshe recognises the words when we say
OL,10,F"Julia's House". She grins from the
OL,11,Fminute we get to the door."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,14,FHealth and Social Care said: "Hospices
OL,15,Fdo incredible work to support people
OL,16,Fand families when they need it most
OL,17,Fand are facing incredibly tough
OL,18,Fpressures.
OL,26,@vD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781732882
OL,3,CMum of girl with rare condition fears
OL,4,Chospice care is at risk over funding
OL,6,F"This government made the biggest
OL,7,Finvestment in hospices in a generation
OL,8,F` #125 million ` to improve hospice
OL,9,Ffacilities, freeing other funding for
OL,10,Fpatient care, and has also committed
OL,11,F#80 million for children's and young
OL,12,Fpeople's hospices over three years.
OL,14,F"In Autumn 2026, we will publish a new
OL,15,Fframework to modernise and improve the
OL,16,Fpalliative and end-of-life care
OL,17,Fsector, as we shift more healthcare
OL,18,Fout of hospitals and into the
OL,19,Fcommunity, with hospices playing a
OL,20,Fcentral role in delivering care closer
OL,21,Fto home."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
